Tingnan mo,

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:03.490
bakit ba ang tanga-tanga nito,

00:22:03.750 --> 00:22:04.860
at lumilipad sa iyong mukha?

00:22:09.830 --> 00:22:10.420
Direktor Jiang,

00:22:11.110 --> 00:22:11.730
ayos ka lang?

00:22:40.200 --> 00:22:40.660
Ayos lang ako.

